data.title: La Vida de Koharu Kusumi
data.meta_description: La Vida de Koharu Kusumi - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Koharu Kusumi is a Japanese singer, actress, television personality, and model. She was a member of the idol group Morning Musume from 2005 to 2009. As an actress, she voiced the main character Kirari Tsukishima in the anime Kirarin Revolution from 2006 to 2009. Following her graduation from Morning Musume, she pursued a modeling career and appeared in television shows. Currently, she hosts radio shows and remains active in music and entertainment.
